{"tid":1075354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主黨：韓國瑜入中聯辦屬禮節性拜訪　毋需過份解讀","createTime":"2019-03-24T05:36:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T11:48:36.000Z","uid":5195,"like":5,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5efb1979562802dbe9337e6cfbb118312dabfb50","tid":1075354,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T05:36:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/309617/%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C%E6%8B%9C%E8%A8%AA%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6-%E6%9E%97%E5%8D%93%E5%BB%B7-%E5%B1%AC%E7%A6%AE%E7%AF%80%E6%80%A7%E6%8B%9C%E8%A8%AA-%E6%AF%8B%E9%9C%80%E9%81%8E%E4%BB%BD%E8%A7%A3%E8%AE%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F309617%2F%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2591%259C%25E6%258B%259C%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2581%25AF%25E8%25BE%25A6-%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%258D%2593%25E5%25BB%25B7-%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E7%25AF%2580%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%258B%259C%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E6%25AF%258B%25E9%259C%2580%25E9%2581%258E%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E8%25AE%2580&d=6SPFYKHnGSG2Q49qavPU8t6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=4e1b2d81\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/309617/%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C%E6%8B%9C%E8%A8%AA%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6-%E6%9E%97%E5%8D%93%E5%BB%B7-%E5%B1%AC%E7%A6%AE%E7%AF%80%E6%80%A7%E6%8B%9C%E8%A8%AA-%E6%AF%8B%E9%9C%80%E9%81%8E%E4%BB%BD%E8%A7%A3%E8%AE%80</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣高雄市長韓國瑜昨日（22日）到訪香港時，在未有事先公布的情況下到訪中聯辦，並與中聯辦主任王志民會面，惹來輿論熱議。立法會議員朱凱廸、區諾軒、梁耀忠及香港眾志聯署批評韓國瑜到訪中聯辦並不合適，前立法會議員羅冠聰撰文形容是「死亡之吻」。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員林卓廷在接受《香港01》查詢時，認為韓國瑜與王志民會面屬禮節性拜訪，這些會晤未必反映與對方有緊密的政治聯繫或認同對方的政治主張，「不需要過份解讀」。<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷續指，有時官員外訪也會拜訪當地不同的機關部門同人，與今次韓國瑜與王志民見面性質類同，「不覺得他來香港是為了見中聯辦」。林表示，「客觀來看，他們帶了很多農產品來，推銷農產品，這是事實，至於他有沒有其他的考慮，就要看他自己了」。<br />\n<br />\n他又舉例說，「我們去台灣，有時會見獨派的立委，立委有那麼多人坐在一起，有國民黨、民進黨、有些智庫是獨派的，有甚麼出奇？不代表我認同他。」<br />\n<br />\n最後，林卓廷笑言，「如有機會，希望韓國瑜透過中聯辦留意中央對香港的干預」，又叫他留意香港人對中聯辦的反感。"},{"pid":"5246ad04fab47f4327b546f08ccdc8d7ec297eaa","tid":1075354,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T05:37:32.000Z","msg":"搶咗黃毓民個SPEECH?"},{"pid":"9b696e7e032247e43739a52efa79465f5caf9e3c","tid":1075354,"uid":10680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T05:40:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8fece209ace390d56a88a2d6ce83e2c81c91f21a","tid":1075354,"uid":33907,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T05:41:54.000Z","msg":"咪係 民主黨入中聯辦含下撚架咋 絕對無賣港賣屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d47f4591cb08bda9e000d175a2ab43edcf861be4","tid":1075354,"uid":75072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T05:56:22.000Z","msg":"台灣冇叛國罪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948e2248f81505c513e5fc5a1980bd94331c0730","tid":1075354,"uid":59283,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T06:02:16.000Z","msg":"聞屎黨:無問題呀,因為我地都入過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5e01a22bdd6ee1618b3747004a93f54847115e","tid":1075354,"uid":14478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T06:27:04.000Z","msg":"又美化中聯辦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1debcec306ec4c605b6135962344708e431b8c85","tid":1075354,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"948e2248f81505c513e5fc5a1980bd94331c0730","tid":1075354,"uid":59283,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T06:02:16.000Z","msg":"聞屎黨:無問題呀,因為我地都入過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T06:28:59.000Z","msg":"黃毓民都話無問題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803f4427987b458636dd06de6d14465e8cd53122","tid":1075354,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T06:33:22.000Z","msg":"咁當年又斯斯縮縮驚比人發覺佢地搞密室談判?比人篤爆左先道歉"},{"pid":"bef853411ecf2eee70adc42a1ca9cca878a18f5e","tid":1075354,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T06:36:35.000Z","msg":"民主黨解釋已經無說服力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1539f5e4c79afcfc43b0b10619b9f8bc45c31464","tid":1075354,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bef853411ecf2eee70adc42a1ca9cca878a18f5e","tid":1075354,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T06:36:35.000Z","msg":"民主黨解釋已經無說服力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T06:40:22.000Z","msg":"點解唔係禮義廉出黎講講<br />\n而係my 香港衝出黎幫手解話既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d019d6cbce4d0c127ec89910b40a6131b74e165b","tid":1075354,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T11:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}